    {
      "id": 3391244,
      "is_internal": false,
      "editable": false,
      "type": "Activities::Comment",
      "message": "@diracdeltas, HTTPS everywhere doesn't work on `file:///`, scripts blocking doesn't work on `file:///`.\nDon't know whether it's a separate issue, but this behavior allows MITMing scripts on `file:///` and `chrome://brave/`.",
